description:
&lt;p&gt;This is a 12 month maternity leave cover post but in that time it would be an amazing opportunity to either consolidate or test your paediatric knowledge and skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You would be joining a team of highly specialised therapists providing a broad range of input to numerous clinical specialities. This is a rotational post (every 9 months) and you would be starting in the speciality of acute Neuro-oncology joining a team of physiotherapists, occupational therapists and therapy assistants all very experienced and all willing to support you in developing your paediatric specific skill set.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are wanting to make a difference to the lives of children and young people, have a passion for working with this age group, fancy a challenge and don&#39;t mind a bit of hard work then we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
